"2 pounds fingerling or small Yukon Gold or Yellow Finn potatoes","1 tablespoon plus 1 tsp. salt, divided","3 tablespoons plus 1 tsp. fresh lemon juice, divided","2  bunches chives","2  large sprigs fresh dill","1/4 cup heavy whipping cream","1/4 teaspoon ground white pepper"